# Generated content & SEO assets — recreated by the generator on every build/publish.
# Keeping them out of source control avoids a dirty working tree and prevents empty
# build-time placeholders from being committed and shipped to production.
**/wwwroot/content/index.json
**/wwwroot/navigation-index.json
**/wwwroot/content-metadata.json
**/wwwroot/search-index.json
**/wwwroot/sitemap.xml
**/wwwroot/robots.txt
**/wwwroot/feed.xml
**/wwwroot/og-images/

# Hosting provider config (generated from the --hosting option)
**/wwwroot/_routes.json
**/wwwroot/_headers
**/wwwroot/_redirects
**/wwwroot/vercel.json
**/wwwroot/.nojekyll
